# Deployment modes & cluster managers

## Where the driver + executors land

- **`local[*]`** — one JVM on your laptop; `*` = all cores (this course's mode)
- **Standalone** — Spark's built-in manager; simple, no dependency
- **YARN** — on Hadoop clusters; legacy on-prem
- **Kubernetes** — driver + executors as pods; cloud-native default
- **Databricks** — managed; the manager is hidden behind the platform

## For the exam

- Recognize **each name and what it runs on** — you rarely configure them by hand
